<div class="modal fade" id="customersHelp" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="customersHelpLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="customersHelpLabel">Customers Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Purpose</h6>
                    <p>This screen manages customer records used across the WMS (ownership, visibility, and reporting).</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Index (List)</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Use filters to search by name or email.</li>
                        <li>Sort columns by clicking the header.</li>
                        <li>Use pagination to navigate and change page size.</li>
                        <li>Inactive records are hidden unless explicitly included.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Create</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Click <strong>New Customer</strong> to open the create form.</li>
                        <li>Fill required fields (Name, Email, Date of Birth).</li>
                        <li>Submit to create and redirect to the Details page.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Edit</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Open a customer and click <strong>Edit</strong>.</li>
                        <li>Update fields and save changes.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Details</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Use <strong>Details</strong> to review full record data.</li>
                        <li>From Details, you can navigate to Edit or Deactivate.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Deactivate</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Click <strong>Delete</strong> to deactivate (soft delete) the customer.</li>
                        <li>Deactivated records can be included via filters.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h6>Common Issues</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li><strong>Email already in use:</strong> Use a unique email per customer.</li>
                        <li><strong>Validation errors:</strong> Check required fields and formats.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-light border" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
